&lt;li&gt;Maintain infrastructure-as-code for deploying resources on Kubernetes across multiple clouds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in design reviews, code reviews, and on-call rotations. Work collaboratively as a member of a cross-functional team to build end-to-end customer experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate full lifecycle ownership of the products and features built, including writing documentation, manual and automated testing.&lt;/li&gt;
